      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and professionally detailed regularly. The exterior paint retains its original factory luster with zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, and all electronic systems, including the navigation and climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive service history and a recent multi-point inspection confirming its peak performance. With low original miles and a smoke-free, pet-free history, this car offers the experience of a brand-new vehicle. Serious buyers are invited to inspect this masterpiece in person to appreciate its flawless state and verifiable maintenance pedigree.",
